data.summary_suggestion: Query current user experience metrics for a website
data.description_suggestion: Queries the Chrome UX Report to retrieve current performance metrics for a given website. Accepts a QueryRequest containing the URL and optional dimensions (form factor, effective connection type). Returns a QueryResponse containing a Record with one or more MetricTimeseries objects representing real user experience data including percentiles, distribution bins, and performance statistics. Use this endpoint for point-in-time performance data; use queryHistoryRecord for historical trends.
